re an Studierende und an Forschende der Literatur-, Musik- und Geschichtswissenschaft ebenso wie an Praktiker der alten Musik.  aIssued also in print.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 06. Mrz 2024) 4aEdition. 4aMinnesang. 4aOswald von Wolkenstein. 7aLITERARY CRITICISM / European / General.2bisacsh  aMinnesang.  aOswald von Wolkenstein.  aedition.1 aBrunner, Horst, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aWachinger, Burghart, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus DeG Package 2024 Part 1z97831113321920 cprintz978311134214640uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978311134231340uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783111342313423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783111342313/original  a978-3-11-133219-2  DG Plus DeG Package 2024 Part 1b2024  aEBA_CL_LT  aEBA_CL_MUAR  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles